{
  "stem": "4513.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was some kind of relationship built between our principal and those other principals that allowed us to debate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I did have, in high school, did have the interaction with white kids in the debating team.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we used to debate all the time with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were-- most of the things we debated around were Americanism, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how to be a good citizen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Talked about, also, about building a nation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we talked about issues, such as during the Roosevelt Administration, it was about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we would talk about things that would happen-- in terms of issues that came out of the Roosevelt Administration-- social security, welfare, public housing, all those things, we were debating.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And most of it came out of the Roosevelt Administration.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very-- I think except as I say, reading it was nonexistent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It just never occurred, we just never knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first time, I remember Pearl Harbor Day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was my first semester in Purdue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So December the 7th, we were, we were at International House.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember I was playing cards with some guys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, one of the young ladies who-- one of the black young ladies, Naomi McElwain, came running in the room, talking about they just bombed Pearl Harbor.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we immediately said, Pear, where the hell is Pearl Harbor?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody knew except this crazy German nationalist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He knew where Pearl Harbor was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told us where Pearl Harbor was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was in Hawaii.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said, why anybody want to bomb there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we sat there talking for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went on about the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we kept saying, you can ignore if you want to.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
